        "client_msg_id": "b5673239-3246-4864-8e0c-a3fda241a9d2",
        "text": "One thought on the \"integrated AI companion\": Coding assistants may have been low hanging fruit, because it's relatively easy to extract context to provide to the AI system. For other systems, I suspect event-driven architectures may become more popular: they may allow for building that context on-the-fly to provide to the AI.",
